{
  "stem": "1419.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we came to, to Birkenau the next day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not-- it was not too, too bad, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were still-- everybody was still healthy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in Birkenau we stayed, I think, a couple or three days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Two days.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we went by foot then, again, to Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was the death march really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the beginning of the death march.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was already snow, full of snowfall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then we had to walk up to Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And lots of people already couldn't make it, not maybe from our group, from some other groups, because we already-- a larger transport was not on our transport.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was a lot of people going from, from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a lot of people couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were already shot on the-- on the road to Gleiwitz, right on the-- right on the spot in the snow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we came to Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We stayed overnight in Gleiwitz in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then they, they load us on the-- on the open railroad cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were-- we were traveling for about a week through-- I don't know-- through Czechoslovakia toward Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were traveling for seven, eight days without food, without--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just traveling, I guess.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they told us later on-- I don't know-- there were rumors that some camps wouldn't accept us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were over filled or something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mauthausen wouldn't accept us or some places, Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the destination we ended up in Sachsenhausen, which is outside of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once in a while, they threw some bread up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- we were-- I don't know how many, 80 or 100 people on there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
